    <item>
      <title>Available Today: Bassist-Composer Matthew Rybick’s Debut Release – Driven – Featuring Ron Blake, Gerald Clayton, Freddie Hendrix, Ulysess Owens Jr. &amp;  Michael Dease</title>
      <link>http://crossharpchronicles.wordpress.com/2011/02/08/available-today-bassist-composer-matthew-rybickis-debut-release-driven-featuring-ron-blake-gerald-clayton-freddie-hendrix-ulysses-owens-jr-michael-dease/</link>
